---
title: "Home"
---

<div class="modal fade" id="modalPicture" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modalPicture" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-2 pt-3 ml-auto pr-5">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>            
        </div>        
        <div class="modal-body">
            <div class="row">
                <img class="modal-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="" alt="Painting">
            </div>
            <h3 class="modal-image-title py-4 color-grape"></h3>
            <p class="modal-image-description col-10 font-weight-bold mx-auto color-grape"></p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid no-padding">
    <ul class="nav">
        <li class="nav-item">Arte Al√©m do Tempo</li>
        <li class="nav-item ml-auto">Terezinha Dreher</li>
    </ul>    


    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-10 col-sm-12 mx-auto mt-5">
        <div class="text-center">
            <img class="img-fluid img-thumbnail" src="{{imagem}}" alt="Terezinha Dreher">
            <h4 class="pt-4">{{artista}}</h4>
            <p>{{especialidade}}</p>
        </div>        
        <p>{{descricao}}</p>
    </div>    

    <hr class="alert-success my-5"/>

    <div class="col-6 mx-auto">
        <p>Por favor, clique em algum dos quadros abaixo para ver uma imagem maior.</p>
    </div>    

    <div class="row col-md-10 col-sm-12 mx-auto pt-5">        
        {{#each paintings}}
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card card-inverse mx-auto mb-5" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalPicture" style="width: 20rem;">
                    <img class="card-img" src="{{this.path}}" alt="Card">
                    <div class="card-img-overlay">
                        <h4 class="card-title" data-description={{this.description}}>{{this.title}} <span class='float-right icon'>&#9906;</span></h4>                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>
